snippet.title: Batman: Arkham Knight - WayneTech Track Pack
snippet.description:
Batman: Arkham Knight - WayneTech Track Pack (Batmobile AR Challenges) gameplay in Full HD (1080p)

0:00 - Batmobile Race: Batmobile Proving Ground - 1 Lap Race (2016 Batman v Superman Batmobile)
0:48 - Batmobile Race: Batmobile Proving Ground - 3 Lap Race (Robin Themed Batmobile)
2:48 - Batmobile Race: WayneTech - Loop (Riddler Themed Batmobile)

===================================

Game available on: Sony PlayStation 4, Microsoft Xbox One & PC
Video recorded on: PC
